

Works on iOS 6

Requested by reddit user /u/cheopsrule. Quite convenient. Swipe up/down on album cover artwork to adjust volume. Swipe left/right for previous/next song. Easy as that. Not sure about the use, though.
No settings to configure. No screenshots for this product.

